translations.Expected filesize of %1$s but read (from: Expected filesize of %1$s but read (from MagentaCLOUD client) and wrote (to MagentaCLOUD storage) %2$s. Could either be a network problem on the sending side or a problem writing to the storage on the server side.

translations.End to end encryption is currently enabl: End to end encryption is currently enabled.
translations.Please read carefully before resetting y: Please read carefully before resetting your end-​to-​end encryption keys
translations.Once your encryption keys are reset, all: Once your encryption keys are reset, all encrypted data will be inaccessible and will be also deleted.
translations.Before you reset your encryption, check: Before you reset your encryption, check your apps and desktop clients to make sure you really can not access your keys anywhere.
translations.If you want to reset the encryption even: If you want to reset the encryption even though your keys are still available in the apps or desktop clients, then delete the keys locally on the other devices. Alternatively, you can reset the apps or reconnect the desktop clients to your account.
translations.This the final warning: Do you really wa: This the final warning: Do you really want to reset your encryption. Encrypted data are lost and will be deleted.
translations.End to end encryption is currently disab: End-to-end encryption is currently disabled. You can set it up with MagentaCLOUD clients.

translations.You can create links or send shares by m: You can create links or send shares by mail. If you invite MagentaCLOUD users, you have more opportunities for collaboration.
translations.With File drop, only uploading is allowe: With File drop, only uploading is allowed. Only you can see files and folders that have been uploaded.
translations.There are no editing functions for files: There are no editing functions for files shared with non-MagentaCLOUD users.
translations.The password is not sent with the email: The password is not sent with the email to maintain confidentiality.
translations.is Telekom's secure and free online stor: is Telekom's secure and free online storage. Ideal for your photos, videos and any other files you want to store securely. You can upload your data directly from your smartphone, tablet or PC, access it from anywhere and easily share it with family and friends.
You can attach a message to the share.
translations.The password must contain 10 characters: The password must contain 10 characters and will not be sent with the mail to maintain confidentiality.
